\begin_layout Problem*
用拉普拉斯展开式, 交换环
\begin_inset Formula $R$
\end_inset

上可以定义行列式.
 设
\begin_inset Formula $A=(a_{ij})$
\end_inset

为
\begin_inset Formula $R$
\end_inset

上得
\begin_inset Formula $n\times n$
\end_inset

矩阵(
\begin_inset Formula $n>1$
\end_inset

).
 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{ij}$
\end_inset

为
\begin_inset Formula $(i,j)$
\end_inset

-代数余子式, 则
\begin_inset Formula $\det(A_{ij})=(\det A)^{n-1}$
\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Solution*
证明: 若
\begin_inset Formula $R=\ZZ$
\end_inset

, 这是线性代数的结论.
 任意的
\begin_inset Formula $R$
\end_inset

都是
\begin_inset Formula $\ZZ$
\end_inset

-代数, 由多元多项式代数的泛性, 存在
\begin_inset Formula $\ZZ$
\end_inset

-代数同态
\begin_inset Formula $f:\ZZ[x_{ij}\mid1\le i,j\le n]\to R$
\end_inset

使得
\begin_inset Formula $f(x_{ij})=a_{ij}$
\end_inset

(
\begin_inset Formula $1\le i,j\le n$
\end_inset

).
 这就给出
\begin_inset Formula $R$
\end_inset

中的等式
\begin_inset Formula $\det(A_{ij})=(\det A)^{n-1}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

